Subject: [PATCH 2/4] translate: move runtime data and TM storage to user dir

Move GUI runtime state and translation-memory storage out of the repository.

This change makes the GUI load and save batch queue and progress cache through
user-scoped runtime paths, and moves the translation-memory database to the
same application directory. It also adds WAL mode and a re-entrant lock around
SQLite access to make future threaded access less fragile.

The main effect is to stop polluting the repository with mutable files and make
state handling more consistent across platforms.

